    "Third, the relatively small number of participants in the expert study limits the generalizability of the results.",
    "Conducting a larger crowdsourced user study would be beneficial in verifying the quality of the automated output further and investigating the factors that contribute to users' perceived quality.The performance of LLMs in VA tasks: While LLM exhibits potentials, some of the limitations of LLM requires careful handling.• Output stability and accuracy: The output of LLMs can be unstable.",
    "During our evaluation, we encountered instances where the model failed to follow instructions accurately, leading to parsing and execution failures in the generated code.",
